attributes.Long form description: The student begins to turn the rashult over and begins to disassemble the four wheels and leaves one by one on the table. Once the wheels are disassembled, the student turns the rashult over to disassemble the first tray, which he places on the table when finished. The student proceeds to disassemble the middle tray which he places on the table when finished. The student proceeds to disassemble the bottom tray and stacks it on top of the other trays. The student proceeds to disassemble the first side bars of the rashault. The student disassembles the second side bars. The student disassembles the third side bars. The student disassembles the fourth side bar. Finally, the student separates and stacks the base frames on the table, leaving the furniture disassembled.
